00:51:04.800 --> 00:51:07.360
Even though I'm not afraid
or disgusted that Nawa is a merman,

00:51:09.500 --> 00:51:12.310
I just don't know how to
handle this relationship.

00:51:13.710 --> 00:51:16.650
I don't know what's appropriate
and in appropriate,

00:51:18.290 --> 00:51:19.430
right or wrong anymore

00:51:23.770 --> 00:51:26.040
especially since Nawa decided
to live with his own kind.

00:51:29.230 --> 00:51:30.600
You'll never truly know

00:51:31.340 --> 00:51:32.890
how he feels unless you

00:51:33.240 --> 00:51:34.620
hear it from him directly.

00:51:35.190 --> 00:51:36.740
And about what you said

00:51:37.090 --> 00:51:39.020
that you don't know how to
handle the relationship

00:51:39.720 --> 00:51:40.770
that's not strange at all.

00:51:41.520 --> 00:51:44.130
My mother felt the same way.

00:51:47.640 --> 00:51:48.790
In the past...

00:51:49.420 --> 00:51:52.840
I used to think she hated me
because I was a merman.

00:51:54.050 --> 00:51:56.380
But after we talked, I understood that

00:51:56.900 --> 00:51:59.560
she just didn't know how to deal
with the fact that her son was one.

00:52:01.480 --> 00:52:02.500
Even now,

00:52:02.980 --> 00:52:06.770
I still don't know how to deal
with all this.

00:52:07.860 --> 00:52:11.400
But one thing I do know
is how much I love you, my son.

00:52:15.060 --> 00:52:16.210
I love you, Ping.

00:52:18.780 --> 00:52:21.310
I can't bear to lose you.

00:52:28.500 --> 00:52:30.110
Then let's start over again, Mom.

00:52:36.110 --> 00:52:37.460
You have to ask yourself,

00:52:38.350 --> 00:52:40.670
do you love Nawa enough?

00:52:42.110 --> 00:52:43.970
Because if you can't stand
the thought of losing him,

00:52:44.530 --> 00:52:47.970
then stop worrying about
how to handle the relationship.

00:52:49.200 --> 00:52:49.940
Sometimes,

00:52:50.700 --> 00:52:52.630
feelings have to come before reason.

00:52:57.070 --> 00:52:57.950
Mr. Phurit.

00:52:58.700 --> 00:53:00.520
If I tell you the truth,

00:53:01.730 --> 00:53:03.090
can you promise me one thing?

00:53:05.150 --> 00:53:06.560
Promise you won't leave me.

00:53:09.160 --> 00:53:09.880
Nawa…

00:53:11.930 --> 00:53:13.040
I don't know

00:53:13.900 --> 00:53:15.990
what you're about to tell me,

00:53:20.010 --> 00:53:21.140
but I promise

00:53:23.240 --> 00:53:24.640
I'll stay by your side no matter what.

00:53:27.590 --> 00:53:32.090
And one more thing,
I truly believe that if Nawa had a choice,

00:53:32.600 --> 00:53:34.740
he'd still want to live his life with you.

00:53:39.390 --> 00:53:43.160
Thank you, Ping.
You made me realize something.

00:53:45.440 --> 00:53:48.100
The rest is up to you now, Mr. Phurit.

00:53:54.340 --> 00:53:56.760
Have you ever seen one, then?

00:53:58.670 --> 00:54:00.000
For this question,

00:54:00.730 --> 00:54:02.730
I'll answer that question the day you truly

00:54:03.180 --> 00:54:04.540
believe mermen exist.

00:54:14.540 --> 00:54:15.820
I think I know now, Ping.

00:54:57.550 --> 00:54:58.440
Why are you here?

00:54:59.570 --> 00:55:00.560
I know the truth now.

00:55:02.130 --> 00:55:03.400
Where did you take Nawa?

00:55:05.250 --> 00:55:06.130
You really want to know?

00:55:07.780 --> 00:55:08.780
Then step over my dead body first.

00:55:29.170 --> 00:55:31.010
(Love each other.)

00:55:32.840 --> 00:55:34.760
(Complicated.)

00:55:36.860 --> 00:55:38.280
(My world.)

00:55:39.160 --> 00:55:41.850
(A new world together.)

00:55:47.200 --> 00:55:50.250
(underline it as forbidden love.)

00:55:50.850 --> 00:55:52.710
(Next Episode)
If Nawa and I truly can't be together,

00:55:53.280 --> 00:55:55.840
then that decision should be ours

00:55:56.320 --> 00:55:57.510
not anyone else's.

00:55:57.930 --> 00:56:01.020
You really think this problem
is that simple to fix?

00:56:04.000 --> 00:56:06.570
You called for me, headman.
What do you need me to do?

00:56:07.430 --> 00:56:09.520
Take this information to
the humans who hunt mermen.

00:56:10.210 --> 00:56:13.280
Once they kill the mermen,
make sure you kill the humans too.

00:56:14.410 --> 00:56:15.380
Leave no evidence behind.

00:56:24.330 --> 00:56:27.260
Grandpa Samut, please help Mr. Phurit!
I don't know what's happening to him!

00:56:27.480 --> 00:56:29.390
This man has been poisoned
by a merman's poison.

00:56:29.700 --> 00:56:30.790
To save him,

00:56:30.930 --> 00:56:34.140
he must drink the blood
from a merman's heart.

00:56:35.610 --> 00:56:37.310
I hope what I'm about to do

00:56:39.060 --> 00:56:41.370
can repay the love you've given me.

00:56:43.520 --> 00:56:44.550
I love you, Mr. Phurit.

